&lt;p&gt;JOB FUNCTION: The Buyer is responsible for executing purchasing activities, managing supplier relationships, and ensuring timely delivery of materials to meet business needs. The ideal candidate is detail-oriented, responsive, and thrives in a fast-paced, operationally focused environment.&amp;nbsp; This role is an individual contributor and works on-site at our Solon, OH headquarters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JOB DUTIES&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute purchase orders in alignment with demand requirements and inventory targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor open orders and proactively manage delivery schedules to ensure on-time fulfillment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate regularly with suppliers to confirm pricing, lead times, and order status.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resolve discrepancies related to shipments, pricing, invoicing, and quality issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with Operations, Finance and Engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate and current purchasing data within ERP system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support cost savings initiatives and continuous improvement efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and mitigate supply chain risks, including delays or shortages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in sourcing activities as needed, including RFQs and supplier evaluations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs other duties and activities in support of the business as necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;KNOWLEDGE &amp;amp; SKILLS:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates strong mathematical and analytical skills; and is proactive in problem-solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has solid understanding of negotiation, purchasing and inventory management principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicates effectively both in writing and in-person; Can build and foster relationships with suppliers and our internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has strong organizational ability with attention to detail and sense of urgency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates proficiency with Microsoft Office applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates proficiency with ERP/MRP systems (NetSuite, SAP, Infor, or similar).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shows ability to manage multiple projects and adapt to changing priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;EDUCATION &amp;amp; EXPERIENCE:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Required: Meets one of the following
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s Degree in Supply Chain, Business, Finance or other related field from an accredited institution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Associate’s Degree in Business, Finance or related field from an accredited institution AND 3 years of related experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 years of experience as a Buyer in lieu of a degree.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferred: Prior experience in a manufacturing or distribution environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is responsible for setup and operating CNC production machines to manufacture parts to meet customer orders. The CNC Setup Operator will prepare machines for production runs, ensure proper tooling and offsets, and monitor performance to maintain quality and efficiency. We offer a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;148&quot; data-end=&quot;182&quot;&gt;competitive shift differential&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;for applicable schedules, along with&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;220&quot; data-end=&quot;246&quot;&gt;overtime opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;based on business needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Duties:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ewqoi4&quot; data-start=&quot;708&quot; data-end=&quot;800&quot;&gt;Set up CNC machines, including installing tooling, fixtures, and materials for production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;367mu4&quot; data-start=&quot;801&quot; data-end=&quot;881&quot;&gt;Operate CNC production equipment to meet customer orders and production goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;w69xxr&quot; data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1055&quot;&gt;Plan machining by studying work orders, blueprints, material specifications, drawings, surface locations, and machining parameters; interpreting dimensions and tolerances.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1uujvtj&quot; data-start=&quot;1056&quot; data-end=&quot;1139&quot;&gt;Adjust machine offsets, speeds, and feeds to ensure parts meet quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1r3j938&quot; data-start=&quot;1140&quot; data-end=&quot;1227&quot;&gt;Perform basic troubleshooting and make minor adjustments to maintain production flow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;yfa8os&quot; data-start=&quot;1228&quot; data-end=&quot;1290&quot;&gt;Maintain production equipment to meet customer requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;hf0dq4&quot; data-start=&quot;1291&quot; data-end=&quot;1367&quot;&gt;Maintain safe operations by adhering to safety procedures and regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;a3ju5f&quot; data-start=&quot;1368&quot; data-end=&quot;1506&quot;&gt;Maintain equipment by completing preventive maintenance requirements; following manufacturer instructions; troubleshooting malfunctions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;zt8z1h&quot; data-start=&quot;1507&quot; data-end=&quot;1623&quot;&gt;Maintain continuity among work shifts by documenting and communicating actions, irregularities, and ongoing needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;k1c87m&quot; data-start=&quot;1624&quot; data-end=&quot;1675&quot;&gt;Maintain accurate production and quality records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;kfsr8w&quot; data-start=&quot;1676&quot; data-end=&quot;1726&quot;&gt;Maintain a safe, clean, and organized work area.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills and Knowledge:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic math&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blueprint reading&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of G and M codes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize various measuring gages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail and communication skills, oral and written.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education and Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School diploma or equivalent required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 2 years experience as a CNC machine operator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
